pageContext.claim: “The Obama Administration is turning out to be one of the most corrupt and incompetent in U.S. history. Remember, he and Sleepy Joe are the reasons I am in the White House!!!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump may not be a fan, but no senior advisors or officials from the Obama administration— unlike other previous administrations —  were indicted on corruption charges. So, it is tough to make the case that either Obama or his administration was the “most corrupt” in U.S. history.
